  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Orthopedic tibial tray FEA credibility assessment (NC-4 clean package)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for finite element analysis (FEA) of tibial tray stress distribution in a total knee arthroplasty (TKA) implant system. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict peak von Mises stress in the tibial tray under physiological gait loading for a Class II orthopedic device at Model Risk Level 3. All 13 credibility factors are fully assessed; achievedLevel meets or exceeds requiredLevel for every factor. Decision: Accepted.",
